# Paths excluded from the deployment source.
#
# ⚠ Patterns follow .gitignore semantics: a bare name is UNANCHORED and matches
# at any depth. `data` matches src/lib/data/ as well as ./data. Every directory
# pattern below is therefore anchored with a leading slash so it can only match
# at the repository root. Do not remove those slashes.
#
# Anything the browser loads lives in public/ and must never be listed here.

# Source material the application never imports — docs/assets alone is ~11 MB
# of client PDFs, and brand-assets/ holds 30 unprocessed logo originals.
/docs
/brand-assets

# CI config and Lighthouse budgets play no part in a Vercel build.
/.github
/lighthouserc.json
